<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Bowdeen</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-07-26 15:16:00</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>My group and I took out the entire Kaesora zone on Friday. Both times in here there has been no one, so we could choose what we wanted to camp. Of course we picked the church since the sword as well as the fangs drop here (+ other items)(fangs are for a quest to obtain keys into howling stones). I was the lucky winner on the Blade random, to this day I still use my 2sh mithril. Why the mith you might ask, because I don't have a haste belt/sash so without that I deal more damage over time with my mith. Once I get a haste Item I will definatly change seeing how this is probally the best 2sh avail to myself (lvl 40) until I can goto CoM, Sebelis or Chardok.<BR>
This zone rocks for items of all classes of the mid-level range.</font></td></tr></table>
